translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「別に駄目じゃない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's not that it's bad."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ただ、乳久里ちゃんはなんというか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's just, Nyukuri-chan is how should I put it..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: セックスが好きとは少し違う気がする」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I feel it's a little different from simply liking sex."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうさねぇ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well then..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ま、確かに最近のそれは慈善事業だねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, it's true that lately, it's been like a charity work."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うーん、なんと言ったもんか……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm, how should I say it..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 更におちょこを傾ける。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She tilted the sake cup further.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乳久里の瞳は酒に酔い、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nyukuri's eyes, drunk from the sake,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とろんと目尻が下がっていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: were glazed over and the corners of her eyes drooped.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「男と一夜を共にするのが好きなのは本当さ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's true that I like spending a night with a man."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でも、確かに兄さんみたいに性行為が
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But surely, it's not like I like sex as much as you do, big brother."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 好きってわけじゃないんだろうねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's not exactly the case."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちょいと、昔の話になるんだけどねぇ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well then, this will be a little story from long ago, okay?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乳久里がそっと視線を空に投げ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nyukuri gently cast her gaze toward the sky,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスもつられて空を見上げた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Rance followed suit, looking up at the sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あたしに癒し巫女としての才能はなくってねぇ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I had no talent as a healing shrine maiden, you see.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 出来ることは戦巫女――戦闘の仕事と、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What I could do was a warrior shrine maiden—combat work,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あとは隠密の真似事だけだった」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and then just mimicry of stealth work."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「他の子達とは理由こそ違うし、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Though the reasons were different from the other girls,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 誰に強制されたわけでもないけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and I wasn't forced by anyone...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしも色んな男に抱かれてね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was embraced by various men too."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それを嫌だと思ったことはないし、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I never thought that was unpleasant,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 必要なことだと思ってきた……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I believed it was necessary...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちっとは誇らしい気持ちになったことだって」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There were even times I felt a little proud of it."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でも、でもねぇ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But, but you see..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「惚れた男と一緒になれるかもって時、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "When I thought I might be able to be with a man I loved,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしの仕事を聞かれて答えた時――」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and I was asked about my work and gave my answer—"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あの、婚約破棄される時の言葉……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The words from when the engagement was broken off...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 汚いものを見る目がねぇ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The look in his eyes as if he was seeing something filthy,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしの耳と瞼の裏に貼り付いちまった……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: stuck in my ears and behind my eyelids..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それ以来、本気にならず、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Since then, I haven't taken anything seriously,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 適度な距離感の相手と恋愛ごっこさ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: just playing at love with partners at a reasonable distance."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一時だけでいいのさ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Just for a moment, that's enough...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一時だけ愛されりゃ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If I'm loved for just a moment,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしは自分の輪郭を失わずに済む」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can keep from losing my sense of self."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「沢山の男と寝る理由ってなぁ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The reason I sleep with many men is...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんなところかねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: probably something like that."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、当時はショックだったが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, it was a shock at the time,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 誰彼構わず寝る女が汚いってなぁ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but the idea that a woman who sleeps with anyone is dirty,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そう間違いでもないかなと思うけどね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I don't think that's entirely wrong."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「乳久里ちゃんはちっとも汚くないぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Nyukuri-chan is not dirty at all.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: むしろ綺麗だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If anything, she's beautiful."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふふ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hehe...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いいこと言うねぇ、兄さん」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You say nice things, big brother."
"Oh?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乳久里がそっと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nyukuri gently,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの腕にもたれかかり頭を乗せる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: leaned on Rance's arm and rested her head on it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なあ……兄さん？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey... big brother?"
